[[File:Wish_plant.jpg|thumb|200px|The [[Leaf Queen]]'s wish plant.]]

A '''wish plant''' was a kind of plant that would seemingly give someone any object they wished for. Excessive granting of wishes would severely affect the plant's health. However, tears cried onto the plant could bring it back to full verdure.<ref name="2-02">{{Ewoks|The Wish Plant}}</ref>

The [[Leaf Queen]] owned a wish plant which she once left in the care of [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]].<ref name="2-02" />

